---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
    title="Tentang Kami"
    description="Pelajari visi, misi, dan filosofi SyntaxTrust dalam membangun solusi teknologi yang aman, cepat, dan visioner bagi institusi pendidikan dan korporasi."
>
    <!-- Header Section -->
    <section class="pt-48 pb-20 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
            <div class="text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto">
                <span
                    class="text-syntax-emerald font-black tracking-[0.4em] uppercase block mb-6 text-xs reveal-on-scroll"
                    >Filosofi & Visi</span
                >
                <h1
                    class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-black mb-10 tracking-tighter leading-tight reveal-on-scroll"
                >
                    Membangun Kepercayaan Melalui <span class="gradient-text"
                        >Integritas Kode</span
                    >
                </h1>
                <p
                    class="text-gray-400 text-xl md:text-2xl leading-relaxed font-medium reveal-on-scroll"
                    style="transition-delay: 200ms;"
                >
                    SyntaxTrust hadir sebagai mitra teknologi yang tidak hanya
                    fokus pada hasil akhir, tetapi sangat memuja detail dalam
                    setiap baris algoritma.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div
            class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[50%] h-[50%] bg-syntax-accent/10 rounded-full blur-[120px] -z-10"
        >
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Content Section -->
    <section class="py-32 relative">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-32 items-center">
                <div class="relative reveal-on-scroll">
                    <div
                        class="absolute -top-16 -left-16 w-64 h-64 bg-syntax-emerald/20 rounded-full blur-[120px]"
                    >
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="relative glass aspect-[4/3] rounded-[4rem] border border-white/10 p-2 transform -rotate-2 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-700"
                    >
                        <img
                            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1451187580459-43490279c0fa?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1200"
                            alt="Arsitektur Teknologi"
                            class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-[3.8rem] opacity-60"
                        />
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="absolute -bottom-10 -right-10 glass p-10 rounded-[3rem] border border-white/10 shadow-3xl reveal-on-scroll"
                        style="transition-delay: 300ms;"
                    >
                        <p class="text-4xl font-black text-syntax-emerald mb-2">
                            100%
                        </p>
                        <p
                            class="text-[10px] text-gray-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest"
                        >
                            Kepuasan Klien
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="space-y-12">
                    <div
                        class="reveal-on-scroll"
                        style="transition-delay: 150ms;"
                    >
                        <h2
                            class="text-4xl font-black text-white mb-6 tracking-tight"
                        >
                            Kualitas Adalah Komitmen Utama
                        </h2>
                        <p
                            class="text-gray-400 text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium"
                        >
                            Kami percaya bahwa setiap bisnis memiliki kebutuhan
                            unik. Oleh karena itu, kami menolak pendekatan "satu
                            ukuran untuk semua". Setiap solusi yang kami bangun
                            adalah hasil riset mendalam terhadap tantangan
                            spesifik yang dihadapi klien kami.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div
                        class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8 reveal-on-scroll"
                        style="transition-delay: 300ms;"
                    >
                        <div
                            class="p-8 glass rounded-[2.5rem] border border-white/5 space-y-4"
                        >
                            <div
                                class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-syntax-emerald/10 flex items-center justify-center text-syntax-emerald"
                            >
                                <svg
                                    class="w-6 h-6"
                                    fill="none"
                                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                    stroke="currentColor"
                                    ><path
                                        stroke-linecap="round"
                                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                                        stroke-width="2.5"
                                        d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"
                                    ></path></svg
                                >
                            </div>
                            <h4 class="text-lg font-black text-white">
                                Privasi Prioritas
                            </h4>
                            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                                Keamanan data Anda adalah prioritas non-nego
                                dalam setiap proyek yang kami tangani.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div
                            class="p-8 glass rounded-[2.5rem] border border-white/5 space-y-4"
                        >
                            <div
                                class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-syntax-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center text-syntax-accent"
                            >
                                <svg
                                    class="w-6 h-6"
                                    fill="none"
                                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                    stroke="currentColor"
                                    ><path
                                        stroke-linecap="round"
                                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                                        stroke-width="2.5"
                                        d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"
                                    ></path></svg
                                >
                            </div>
                            <h4 class="text-lg font-black text-white">
                                Performa Ultra
                            </h4>
                            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                                Sistem yang cepat bukan pilihan, melainkan
                                standar dasar untuk setiap produk kami.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Vision CTA -->
    <section class="py-32">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
            <div
                class="glass p-20 rounded-[4rem] border border-white/5 reveal-on-scroll"
            >
                <h2
                    class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black mb-10 tracking-tighter"
                >
                    Siap Memulai <span class="gradient-text"
                        >Transformasi Digital?</span
                    >
                </h2>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-xl mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                    Mari diskusikan bagaimana SyntaxTrust dapat mengakselerasi
                    pertumbuhan bisnis Anda melalui teknologi tepat guna.
                </p>
                <a href="/layanan" class="btn-primary">Lihat Layanan Kami</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
